4. Attribution Requirement: Any derivative work or redistributed version, whether modified or unmodified, must display at least 50% creator credit to the original author in visible branding.

5. Revenue Share Requirement: Any commercial use, sale, subscription, or monetization of this software or its derivative works must provide the original author with 30% of gross revenue earned from the product.

6. You may privately modify and use the software without attribution if it is not redistributed or used commercially.

